text: Darya Vassilyeva (born 14 October 1988) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She was part of the Kazakhstani team at the 2011 World Aquatics Championships, and the 2012 Women's Olympic Qualification Tournament. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
